    "Although DeepSeek-R1-Zero exhibits strong reasoning capabilities, it faces several issues.",
    "DeepSeek-R1-Zero struggles with challenges such as poor readability and language mixing, as DeepSeek-V3 Base is trained on several languages, especially English and Chinese.",
    "To address these issues, we develop DeepSeek-R1, whose pipeline is illustrated in Fig. 2.",
    "In the initial stage, we collect thousands of cold-start data that exhibit a conversational, human-aligned thinking process, as detailed in Supplementary Information, section 2.",
